We re thrilled to launch FaceID a secure biometric tech using facial recognition to protect your data.

We are excited to announce a great new feature for our products! You no longer have to type out your dreams now you can simply record them with your voice! No more struggling with long texts just speak and let our product do the rest. Additionally you can now listen to your dream interpretation rather than just reading it. This makes dream review easier and much more enjoyable. We hope you enjoy this new feature!

We re ecstatic to roll out fresh updates in our app. Streaks Challenge yourself to increase empathy Sharing your dreams and listening to other people s dreams can help to improve your empathy levels. Track your dreams moods for 4 weeks to release your past and get mental health clarity.

Dear Dreamers We have worked hard to provide you with more features and benefits at no extra cost. With this update you can now access Dream Reviews from therapists and Dream Movies free of charge. To make this possible we have implemented an advertisement platform so please bear with us as we strive to give you the best experience possible. We hope you find this new update useful and await your feedback!

We re thrilled to introduce new features in our app: Dream Movie the premier AI driven Dream Visualisation Tool Dream Notes attach notes to your dream for recalling specifics Dream Edit if you recall more details later don t fret modify your dream Experience this new feature today and maximize your dream potential!

We are excited to announce new features on our app: My Progress start tracking your activity now My History you added dreams more than 85 of dreamers 30 day Guest Pass give your friend 30 days of Unlimited Premium Access Try this new feature now and get the most out of your dreams!

Woohoo! We squashed some serious bugs and improved the chat experience with your therapist. Now you can finally ask them all your questions without worrying about technical hiccups. Say goodbye to glitches and say hello to a smooth chat experience!

We are happy to announce the newest version of our DreamApp! This new version comes with many exciting new features including: the ability to share your dream with a therapist information about each of our dream experts so you can select the one that best fits your needs We hope you enjoy the new features and thank you for supporting our application!

Push Notifications To push or not to push that is the question! Never miss new insight! Choose what notifications are the most important to maximize your time and mental health benefit. Want to make sure you are notified when your dream expert sends you a message When a new symbol is added When a new meaning is discovered for your dream Now YOU choose what matters! Dream Data The power of community! Now you can see even more information about exactly what your dreams are telling you. Because DreamApp has the largest database of collected dreams in the world you will know how common your dreams are and what caused these dreams in other people so you know exactly what steps you need to take next! Dream Page Capture the details DreamApp has heard your request and we have added many new opportunities to record your dream details. Now you can record the date location sleep duration and even images that help you capture in vivid detail all the elements of your dream. This will spark new insight and help you gain the most impactful realizations from every dream you have.
We follow your advice. This is significant performance improvement.

Mood Tracking How are you feeling Every time you sleep you dream. However when we lose touch with ourselves and our mental health it can be difficult to remember our dreams. With our mood tracker we can help you reclaim your dreams by helping you focus on yourself. Find the pattern in your emotions and use it to help you plan your next steps. Dream Journal Document Your Journey Watch as the story of your life unfolds before you. DreamApp will keep a personal timeline of every dream you have so you can watch your progress and see how your life has improved through your personal journey. Go back and reference previous dreams for greater insight or watch as the story of your mind changes to reveal how you are growing.
